Phorum Twitter Module

Requirements
=============

This module requires the curl extenstion be compiled into PHP.


Instructions
=============

1. Get a Twitter account at http://twitter.com/

2. Unpack the module package and put the twitter directory
   into the Phorum's mods directory.

3. Go to your Phorum admin and go to Modules in the menu.

4. Click Settings for the Twitter Module.

5. Go to http://dev.twitter.com/apps and register your forum as twitter    
   application. Enter the Consumer key and secret in the Module settings.

6. Go to "My Access Token" on the Twitter page and enter the given access 
   token and access token secret in the Module settings.

7. Decide if you want all posts or just new topics to go to Twitter.

8. Save your settings.

9. Optional: decide from which forum you want tweets to be sent

10. On the main modules page, enable the module.


